### Nutrisoft Backend - Professional API REST Client Tests
### Este archivo permite probar todos los endpoints del API de Professionals usando el plugin REST Client de VSCode
### Especificación OpenAPI: /src/main/resources/openapi/professional-api-v1.yaml

### ====== VARIABLES ======
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api
@token = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE
@professionalId = 650e8400-e29b-41d4-a716-446655440001



### ====== POST ENDPOINTS ======

### 1. Registrar un nuevo profesional (REQUIERE AUTENTICACIÓN + ROL ADMIN)
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/professionals/register
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "email": "doctor@hospital.com",
  "password": "SecurePassword123!",
  "firstName": "Dr. Carlos",
  "lastName": "López",
  "licenseNumber": "LIC-123456",
  "specialization": "Nutrición Deportiva"
}

